Gauteng Premier David Makhura will deliver his State of the Province Address later this morning. • Editor’s note: Livestream above courtesy DStv 403. You can also watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng Premier David Makhura is delivering his State of the Province Address on Monday. It comes just days after the ANC caucus in the provincial legislature held its lekgotla. The caucus resolved to fight corruption and accelerate service delivery, among other things.